  "synopsis": "18-year-old Manami Katagiri has faced hardships his whole life because he had to drop out of middle school and begin working in a factory to take care of his little sister. For reasons he's re-enrolled in high school to better his life but on his first day he encounters a \"princess\" who he claims has never had to work a day in her life. Is it love at first sight? or perhaps a rivalry?\n\n(Source: MU)",
